{"id":232837070,"title":"高雄JPTIP日語學校","content":"不知道身為高雄人想學日文的人有沒有聽過這間補習班，當初覺得是全日文教學所以才來學習，結果班級教室都是滿班擠到不行就算怎麼反應還是會用話術說什麼其他班比你們班人數多之類的…\n明明繳一樣的錢，卻是不一樣的待遇，明明教室位子不夠卻要收超過教室能負荷的人數…\n且報名的時候還欺騙同學，表面上說你們一定要湊到七個人滿班才可以繼續開班下去，實際上早就已經找到其他班級和我們併班！\n\nhttps://i.imgur.com/Fzrpxn5.jpg\n上課書籍有兩本，價錢都不斐就算了，教室的位子剛好12個要我們坐好坐滿，坐到連打開書的空間都不夠，這樣的上課環境，怎麼敢收這麼多人？\n\n奉勸各位有想要來試聽的人深思熟慮！因為他們講的和做的是很不一樣的！","excerpt":"不知道身為高雄人想學日文的人有沒有聽過這間補習班，當初覺得是全日文教學所以才來學習，結果班級教室都是滿班擠到不行就算怎麼反應還是會用話術說什麼其他班比你們班人數多之類的…，明明繳一樣的錢，卻是不一樣的","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"ecc6a486-c4ac-4f76-996d-7dda5dcb8518","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-06T10:56:44.159Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-06T10:56:44.159Z","commentCount":6,"likeCount":8,"tags":[],"topics":["日語","高雄","補習班","日文","jptip"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"語言","forumAlias":"language","school":"南臺科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":7},{"id":"4b018f48-e184-445f-adf1-fc8e04ba09b9","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/Fzrpxn5.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"26e295b2-e26e-4379-968b-cd53edb5fe3d","url":"https://i.imgur.com/Fzrpxn5l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/Fzrpxn5l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/Fzrpxn5l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-06T10:56:44.159Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-06T10:56:44.159Z"},{"id":"26e295b2-e26e-4379-968b-cd53edb5fe3d","url":"https://i.imgur.com/Fzrpxn5.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/Fzrpxn5","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/Fzrpxn5l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-06T10:56:44.159Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-06T10:56:44.159Z"}],"postAvatar":""}